## 🐛 Bug Report

[hidden property](https://github.com/exceljs/exceljs/issues/26) no work

Lib version: 4.4.0

## Steps To Reproduce

the file row 4 is hidden.

[hide-test.xlsx](https://github.com/user-attachments/files/16093090/hide-test.xlsx)


```javascript
const workbookReader = new ExcelJS.stream.xlsx.WorkbookReader(
      localFilePath,
    );
    for await (const worksheetReader of workbookReader) {
      let readRowNum = 1;
      for await (const row of worksheetReader) {
        Logger.debug(
          `${readRowNum} row.hidden ` + (row.hidden ? 'true' : 'false'),
        );
        readRowNum++;
      }
    }
```

console output

```sh
debug: 1 row.hidden false {"timestamp":"2024-07-04 11:47:24"}
debug: 2 row.hidden false {"timestamp":"2024-07-04 11:47:24"}
debug: 3 row.hidden false {"timestamp":"2024-07-04 11:47:24"}
debug: 4 row.hidden false {"timestamp":"2024-07-04 11:47:24"}
debug: 5 row.hidden false {"timestamp":"2024-07-04 11:47:24"}
```
